    <title>New release for Gancio: v1.21.0</title>
    <updated>2024-11-30T10:14:36+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>les/gancio</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href="https://framagit.org/les/gancio/compare/v1.20.0...v1.21.0"&gt;1.21.0&lt;/a&gt; (2024-11-30)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collection filters should include the local instance in "Trusted Instances", fix &lt;a href="https://framagit.org/les/gancio/issues/482"&gt;#482&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href="https://framagit.org/les/gancio/commit/58bbb5483f510f1fc6c7aaffc926fa5cda531d83"&gt;58bbb54&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add isPast icon in event's page too (&lt;a href="https://framagit.org/les/gancio/commit/147ce9a7a8e8e91bd39d253f4e63a68281841a35"&gt;147ce9a&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;show only future events in Tag and Place pages, fix &lt;a href="https://framagit.org/les/gancio/issues/331"&gt;#331&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href="https://framagit.org/les/gancio/commit/fcec5ae75622b9efd7252ab620f81a4d1b5ec951"&gt;fcec5ae&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;use 'en' as default locale, fix &lt;a href="https://framagit.org/les/gancio/issues/481"&gt;#481&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href="https://framagit.org/les/gancio/commit/4e5ffa98457a5627134c3771cfdf82f9cb86d8e0"&gt;4e5ffa9&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://framagit.org/les/gancio/-/releases/v1.21.0" rel="alternate"/>
